## Interactive Feedback

### Hover Lift (cards, product cards, pattern components)
```tsx
<motion.div
  whileHover={{ y: -3, transition: { duration: 0.2, ease: [0, 0, 0.2, 1] } }}
  className="cursor-pointer"
>
```
Pair with `className="transition-shadow duration-200 hover:shadow-md"` for depth.

### Press (buttons, CTAs, icon buttons)
```tsx
<motion.div whileTap={{ scale: 0.97, transition: { duration: 0.1 } }}>
```
Do **not** apply `whileTap` to the shadcn `Button` directly — wrap the container or use CSS `active:scale-[0.97]` instead.

### Icon Button Hover
```tsx
<motion.div whileHover={{ scale: 1.12, transition: { duration: 0.15 } }}>
  <Button size="icon" aria-label="Send message"><ArrowUp size={18} /></Button>
</motion.div>
```

