## Layout Animations

Use the `layout` prop to automatically animate size and position changes — no manual math needed:

```tsx
// Expanding card, growing input, shifting layout on toggle
<motion.div layout transition={{ duration: 0.3, ease: [0.4, 0, 0.2, 1] }}>

// Animating height (e.g., accordion, collapsible)
<motion.div layout="size">
```

**Rule**: When a component changes size or position due to state (not navigation), use `layout` prop instead of manually animating dimensions.

