## Common Mistakes

**❌ DON'T:**
- Animate opacity-only — always pair with y or scale for depth
- Use `ease-in` for entering elements — it starts slow, feels laggy
- Skip `exit` — disappearing without animation is jarring
- Animate 3+ unrelated things at once — stagger or sequence them
- Use `whileHover` on the entire page layout — scope to the interactive element
- Set duration > 300ms for any UI response

**✅ DO:**
- `ease.out` for entries (decelerate to rest = feels natural)
- Stagger lists with `staggerChildren: 0.05` — not longer
- `layout` prop for size/position changes — framer-motion does the math
- Subtle lift (`y: -3`) + shadow transition for hover on cards
- Keep streaming text animation-free — the fill itself is the motion
